name: Me Sew Sweet Ruffled Sunsuits
description:
Cute and comfy for those hot days.  Available in sizes Newborn up to 4T.  Not really intended to be worn swimming, but perfect for frolicking in the sun!

Please specify what size you would like when checking out, thanks!
If your baby is in between sizes please order the larger size :) Options are:
Newborn
3 mo
6 mo
12 mo
18 mo
2T
3T
4T
